Main Free Options:
1. Google AI Studio (aistudio.google.com)
The most reliable free option from a major provider Medium, offering access to Gemini models with no credit card required. You get generous usage limits for prototyping and small-scale applications.

2. OpenRouter
Provides access to 50+ models including DeepSeek, Qwen, and Kimi with one API key DEV Community. Great for experimenting with different models without managing multiple accounts.

3. Groq
Offers lightning-fast inference for smaller models like Llama, Mistral, and DeepSeek DEV Community. Known for exceptional speed on free tier.

4. Hugging Face
Provides serverless inference for thousands of community models. You get a small monthly credit ($0.10) that works well for experimentation with specialized models.

5. Puter.js
Allows developers to provide users with powerful AI capabilities without any API keys or usage restrictions Puter, using a "User-Pays" model.

6. Cohere
Offers production-quality APIs with 20 requests/minute and 1,000 monthly requests on the free tier.
